This paper deals with the efficient implementation of object queries, which is a fundamental problem in database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the transformation of objects and sets into relations, which is a common technique in data structures (cs.DS). The paper proposes an automatic method for maintaining invariants, which is a key concept in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions experiments with distributed algorithms, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC).
